### Step 6: Common Production Issues & Solutions

#### Issue: CORS Errors
**Solution**: Add production URL to Supabase CORS settings
1. Go to Supabase Dashboard > Settings > API
2. Add your production URL to CORS origins

#### Issue: Email Confirmation Required
**Solution**: Either confirm emails or disable confirmation
1. Go to Supabase Dashboard > Authentication > Settings
2. Disable "Enable email confirmations" temporarily

#### Issue: Invalid Site URL
**Solution**: Update Site URL in Supabase
1. Go to Supabase Dashboard > Authentication > Settings
2. Set Site URL to your production URL

#### Issue: Redirect URL Mismatch
**Solution**: Add redirect URLs
1. Go to Supabase Dashboard > Authentication > Settings
2. Add your production URL to redirect URLs

